**Exception flows** (the sad paths — never skip these):
- **E1 — <bad input>**: <what the system does, what the user sees, exit/error state>.
- **E2 — <dependency unavailable>**: <degradation / retry / surfaced error>.
- **E3 — <limit / quota hit>**: <behavior>.

**Field / validation rules**:

| Field | Rule | On violation |
|-------|------|--------------|
| <field> | <type, range, required?, format> | <message / behavior> |

**Acceptance** (Given/When/Then):
- **Given** <…>, **when** <…>, **then** <observable result>.

